      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "window.api.auth\n• connect「」\n• disconnect「」\n• status「」\n\nwindow.api.git\n• scan「」\n• status「」\n• log「」\n• stashes「」\n• worktrees「」\n\nwindow.api.github\n• repos「」\n• issues「」\n• prs「」\n• pipelines「」\n\nwindow.api.gitlab\n• projects「」\n• mrs「」\n• issues「」\n\nwindow.api.ai\n• complete「」\n• status「」\n\nwindow.api.store\n• get「」\n• set「」",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "window.api.auth\n• connect「」\n• disconnect「」\n• status「」\n\nwindow.api.git\n• scan「」\n• status「」\n• log「」\n• stashes「」\n• worktrees「」\n\nwindow.api.github\n• repos「」\n• issues「」\n• prs「」\n• pipelines「」\n\nwindow.api.gitlab\n• projects「」\n• mrs「」\n• issues「」\n\nwindow.api.ai\n• complete「」\n• status「」\n\nwindow.api.store\n• get「」\n• set「」",
