      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "All IPC channels follow this pattern:\n1. Renderer calls window.api.* method\n2. Preload forwards via ipcRenderer.invoke「」\n3. Main process handles via ipcMain.handle「」\n4. Result returns through the same chain",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "All IPC channels follow this pattern:\n1. Renderer calls window.api.* method\n2. Preload forwards via ipcRenderer.invoke「」\n3. Main process handles via ipcMain.handle「」\n4. Result returns through the same chain",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 55,
      "autoResize": true
    }
